{"word":"δογματίζω","slug":"δογματίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δογματίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:δόγμα'><el>δόγμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to decree</i>, <el>δ. τινὰ καλήν</el> <i>to declare</i> her beautiful, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, of persons, <i>to submit to ordinances</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}